emails.subject: RE: Obselet Datasets
emails.body_text:
Cargonave is not updated since March of 2024 because – as the code and name imply – it contains “historic” values.

Even though we are not directly using it into the tradeflow because there was some vessel tracking done on top of it, I would like to keep the historical.

Regarding Australia, Ill let @Léonard Berney <mailto:leonard.berney@dnext.io>  comment, maybe those sources : aaterminals, cbh and Riordan we are gathering it into other datasets already ?

Thanks
